title: Social Media Safety
author: LevelUp
summary: This section contains training modules related to social media and social networking sites, in particular to how users can be more aware of the kinds of information they share over these services and who has access to it. Topics addressed include awareness of websites' terms of service and user data retention, the impacts of online activities in the physical world, and taking advantage of social media sites' ever-changing privacy features.
